import React from 'react' export default function AssociationCard({association}) { const user = association.id_user; return (

{association.name}

{user.last_name}

{user.first_name}

{association.adress.city} - {association.adress.zip_code}

{association.adress.street_number},{association.adress.street}. Quartier : {association.adress.district}

) }
